        public static org.openqa.selenium.WebDriver getPerfectoRemoteWebDriver(String deviceId,
                                                                       DeviceType deviceType,
                                                                       Browser browser,
                                                                       URL remoteUrl)
        Function to return the Perfecto MobileCloud RemoteWebDriver object based on the parameters passed
        Parameters:
        deviceId - The ID of the Perfecto MobileCloud device to be used for the test execution
        deviceType - The DeviceType corresponding to the Device ID passed as input
        browser - The Browser to be used for the test execution
        remoteUrl - The Perfecto MobileCloud URL to be used for the test execution
        Returns:
        The corresponding RemoteWebDriver object
